Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 这些人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸妈妈重要的朋友们
